                            <comment id="14958189" author="eclark" created="Thu, 15 Oct 2015 02:19:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All day off peak would just be equivalent to not configuring that feature. Why someone want to add the extra configuration to not get anything for it?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14958251" author="vrodionov" created="Thu, 15 Oct 2015 03:52:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;24 off peak hours do not make sense. If someone needs more aggressive compaction 24 hours a day - increase &lt;b&gt;hbase.hstore.compaction.ratio&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14958295" author="zghaobac" created="Thu, 15 Oct 2015 04:39:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not config this feature, isOffPeakHour will always be false. It means all day is not off peak.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
